snippet.title: True Crime Sushi
snippet.description: Welcome to True Crime Sushi!  On this channel, we serve up the raw facts.  We give you the straight sashimi, all beautifully presented on a platter.  If you're into current cases, creepy crimes of the past, or just curious about a particular criminal ... this is the place for you.  For more information, photos, and resources, please visit our website:  https://www.TrueCrimeSushi.com!
